videos.description: Miles Bridges gets the rebound then takes it himself to beat the halftime buzzer with a lay-in.
videos.headline: Miles Bridges goes coast to coast to beat the buzzer

videos.description: Michigan State Head Coach Tom Izzo talks about team's foul trouble in the first half.
videos.headline: Tom Izzo helping out the referees

videos.description: Michigan State picks up the loose ball and Lourawls Narin Jr finds Miles Bridges in transition for the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Bridges finishes the one-handed alley-oop from Nairn Jr

videos.description: Miles Bridges flies in for the putback dunk on the missed 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Bridges comes flying in for the one-handed putback dunk

videos.description: Caleb Swanigan hits the jumper in the post with a hand in his face.
videos.headline: Swanigan hits jumper with hand in his face

videos.description: Tom Izzo is unhappy with a missed free throw causing him to  break his clipboard.
videos.headline: Izzo takes out his frustration on his clipboard

videos.description: Caleb Swanigan talks about playing against Michigan State for the first time since he  decommitted and joined Purdue.
videos.headline: Swanigan on playing against Michigan State
